data.meta_description:
25 likes, 0 comments - rogue.boss on May 25, 2024: "Kill Bill: Volume 1 (R - 2003) Uma Thurman | Lucy Liu
A former #assassin, known simply as The #Bride ( #UmaThurman ), wakes from a coma four years after her #jealous ex-lover Bill ( #DavidCarradine ) attempts to murder her on her #wedding day. Fueled by an insatiable #desire for revenge, she #vows to get even with every person who contributed to the loss of her unborn child, her entire wedding #party, and four years of her life. After devising a hit list, #TheBride sets off on her quest, enduring unspeakable injury and unscrupulous enemies.
#killbill #lucyliu

You might not be able to fight like a #samurai, but you can at least die like a samurai.

*For entertainment and motivational purposes only. Please reach out for removal or credit. Not a paid promotion.".
